snippet.title: Sages of Vandaleria | Steam Trailer | indie.io
snippet.description:
Wishlist Sages of Vandaleria now on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2912820/Sages_of_Vandaleria_Rebirth_of_an_Empire

Vandaleria. A fallen empire that has known only misery and hardship since losing its emperor. It needs a savior! Embark on an epic RPG adventure, fighting across land and sky, restoring the ancient religion, and retake your birthright! That is, if you are ready to pay the price.
